{"tid":2252344,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[雞撚完未?] 中共策劃元朗恐襲至今15個月 一名男子於形點商場高叫口號被黨衛軍帶走","createTime":"2020-10-21T11:58:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T11:58:10.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7bbf87b219561d35e1889af1034deeaa0525a2ba","tid":2252344,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T11:58:10.000Z","msg":"元朗721事件15個月 一名男子高叫港獨口號被警員帶走<br />\n<br />\n今日是元朗721暴力襲擊事件發生15個月，一名男子晚上7時許，到元朗形點商場中庭高叫光復香港、時代革命，以及香港獨立等口號，大批警員在場圍起橙帶截查男子，並將男子帶走。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2362653\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2362653&d=z3Qy88JfdbGSADH60DObPTUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=23e51efd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2362653</a>"}]}